{"tid":1285203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌第一post 和理非回合","createTime":"2019-07-04T13:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T14:46:59.000Z","uid":268735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e04a6ab18384fb7ae340b8f8bd9db6e883db3595","tid":1285203,"uid":268735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"利申：垃圾廢中只參加過6月遊行...<br />\n將為人父...立會爸令我非常慚愧....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武過後大家都要休息<br />\n但係一直出去遊行會令和理非卻步<br />\n<br />\n想請教各位連登大俠如何做到民意繼續高漲，遍地開花？<br />\n如果將反佔中既經歷剪成一套約一個鐘既紀錄片<br />\n<br />\n文宣宣傳後，晚上各區球場播放，要重整大家6月一齊既經歷<br />\n<br />\n200萬人呢個紀錄好難再刷新，都好難每次都動員一定數量既人<br />\n咁希望大家只係落一落自己o個區繼續各理非既回合<br />\n唔好令個運動冷卻..."},{"pid":"f22488aadb0854a281ddae23f18730450c2d7aa7","tid":1285203,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f734af1e97aed1fcefb6505163838743fc1afdc","tid":1285203,"uid":268735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<br />\n<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"3feed7cab2609a25693ff938b6dad6bb59b69951","tid":1285203,"uid":268735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n<br />\n我要飲水"},{"pid":"5af6325d064754e9c53aaae34594a86738a6e218","tid":1285203,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VecJSu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVecJSu1.jpg&h=53f04a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FZPNW0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FZPNW0.png&h=462f3b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDsYGg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"